01:41.760 --> 01:47.120
So it's what you learn from your family, from your friends, from your school, your city,

01:47.120 --> 01:51.000
your state, your country, they all have culture that influences you and helps you develop your

01:51.000 --> 02:00.960
culture, activities you participate in, any place that people gather, you develop a culture.

