However, in some cultures that is a rude gesture.

10:00.040 --> 10:04.880
In ancient Rome, it was contrary to popular belief, the symbol that the gladiator should

10:04.880 --> 10:07.920
be put to death.

10:07.920 --> 10:19.360
In addition, in online forums, the definition has begun to modify and it is changing from

10:19.360 --> 10:25.960
