10:25.960 --> 10:34.040
So all of this indicates that symbols, the meaning of symbols drifts over time and space.

10:34.040 --> 10:40.600
Now I moved from the U.S. to Ireland a little over 10 years ago and discovered that there

10:40.600 --> 10:45.200
are two countries separated by a common language.

