17:01.200 --> 17:06.640
had the code in the version control system, so a great benefit there.

17:06.640 --> 17:08.920
Nothing really out of the ordinary.

17:08.920 --> 17:14.000
We also made it safe to disagree.

17:14.000 --> 17:27.960
