17:50.320 --> 17:54.880
we would discuss these issues and we would bring these problems up and talk about them

17:54.880 --> 18:00.240
and that this was okay, it was acceptable and over time they began to open up and to

18:00.240 --> 18:06.720
disagree and to present their perspectives on things and ask questions.

18:06.720 --> 18:13.800
