18:25.840 --> 18:30.560
And this is because if I don't understand what you've said and I'm trying to understand

18:30.560 --> 18:41.880
that, at some point I'm going to ask a question that to you is going to be rude, not acceptable.

18:41.880 --> 18:45.840
