18:45.840 --> 18:49.360
is and what that issue is if we can't talk about it.

18:49.360 --> 18:53.800
So you've got to be able to both ask the indelicate question and you've got to be ready to receive

18:53.800 --> 18:57.280
the indelicate question.

18:57.280 --> 19:04.960
Okay, so the net result here was we established a project culture.

